      <h2 class="teal">Overview</h2><br>

      <p ><img src="http://36.media.tumblr.com/d1130952388f685abc6c5fdc1453dcb7/tumblr_nv8kf0P6hK1ufxoi7o1_1280.jpg" alt="Crime Infographic"></p><br>
      
